===Pronunciation===
אחד / 'echâd / ekh-awd'

===Etymology===
A numeral from H258; 

===Cardinal number===
# Properly united, that is, [[one]]; or (as an ordinal) first: - a, alike, alone, altogether, and, any (-thing), apiece, a certain [dai-] ly, each (one), + eleven, every, few, [[first]], + highway, a man, once, one, only, other, some, together.

